grabación y formatos/ 4.3 Internet/ 4.4 Nuevos instrumentos.<o:p></o:p></span></div><div style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;"><br /><strong>Epílogo:</strong><span class="apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>el siglo XXI, caminos de futuro en la música<o:p></o:p></span></div><div style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;"><br /><span style="font-size: x-small;"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><u>Bibliografía Siglo XX)&nbsp;</u></b><o:p></o:p></span></span></div><div style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;"><span style="font-size: x-small;"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;">BURKHOLDER, J.P.; GROUT, D.J.; PALISCA, C.V.:</span></b><span class="apple-converted-space"><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;">&nbsp;</span></span><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;">Historia de la música occidental</span></i><span class="apple-converted-space"><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;">&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;">VII edición Alianza ed. Madrid, 2008<o:p></o:p></span></span></div><div style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;"><span style="font-size: x-small;"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;">COOK, N. y POPLE, A. (eds.):</span></b><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;">&nbsp;<i>The Cambridge History of Twentieth Music</i>, Cambridge University Press, 2004.<o:p></o:p></span></span></div><div style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;"><span style="font-size: x-small;"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;">DIBELIUS, ULRICH</span></b><spa